      <title>巧克力制造商陷入困境，可可加工量创 2020 年以来新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/chocolatiers-process-least-cocoa-since-2020-as-record-prices-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年最后三个月，欧洲和亚洲的可可研磨量下降，这是迄今为止最强烈​​的信号，表明巧克力制造商正努力应对创纪录的价格和低库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/chocolatiers-process-least-cocoa-since-2020-as-record-prices-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 09:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
